{"hdf602f5dg39f4g4271g9811g6078ab65e864": ["B-by Mordai's eyes, more of them.", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "3df3e3f7-9e4c-41c9-0153-98deefe69c37"], "h9b3cee41gf8d1g4505gb76ag04db3b1d1076": ["B-by Mordai's eyes, another one.", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "3df3e3f7-9e4c-41c9-0153-98deefe69c37"], "hec35cefdg324bg4855g9250g84685c6eb62d": ["My f-friend's blood not enough? Come to rip me open too?", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "3727ba10-3919-dd20-d91b-101cde69e28f"], "h427c6a48g22d8g461bg882fg182e30ff421c": ["In Cr\u00e8che K'liir, a formal greeting begins with a bow.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "2f47e9a0-9a1c-15d2-a290-b493f1da3647"], "h7ed087ebg31ebg4cafgab73g53c59f2d44e3": ["Is this m-monster with you?", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "0aaa03b5-1ec9-b428-9b87-5c526e543b3a"], "hb66ac6bbgeedbg497cg8497g0722173f384f": ["Yes. And I suggest you do as she says.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "15b586c3-5ab0-93df-1909-653947915ea6"], "hf588c7c4ge3a2g426eg80dbg72d9d46e7708": ["Lower.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "982ef5b8-57da-9419-ea81-710568c22783"], "he0234bd3g6835g4506g9919g6567c2f8d76d": ["<i>Wait for the tiefling to obey. </i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "fb4e50d2-a4df-9b75-aba1-07dd1acb39db"], "hed6b0463g8c5fg4a82g8d96gbbc05a02e75e": ["You saw another gith. <i>Where?</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "f75279e1-f2c9-cd4b-b91b-f645e2630736"], "hb8d3a930g02c2g488eg940agbc5db319e30d": ["On the road to Baldur's Gate, near the mountain p-pass.", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "e2fce8b1-611e-4940-542b-00ffe784d0d1"], "h24a34b13gd952g48d9ga6fcg42abf4fe44eb": ["Saw <i>us</i> 'fore we s-saw <i>it.</i> Jammed its b-b-blade through Yul's belly, straight to the other side.", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "cc7747a2-ea4c-4f0c-f6d1-b9b2d669201b"], "h0ef7140bg84b9g408bg815ag61fe5bbd7a91": ["No twisting? Kin must have been in a hurry.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "b0c27345-b413-98c3-dae6-c14364ff779e"], "hccbe2445g67dcg4cd1gbea7gd1f1642c8a3b": ["The map. Show me.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "c7f4a3d1-87e1-a315-4998-478e11514359"], "hde29a244gdd7dg4afcg9f5agc77d3b6d10da": ["Up. You can keep your innards.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "4384a94b-54dd-ab27-9caf-756e87f71f22"], "h7bca8ef6ge2c7g4b19g9ce0g5c8d23677431": ["By the dead gods, are all gith so brutal?", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "2a7d536e-76f7-7f81-c7d6-0f665d903b2c"], "he40ae16dga377g41c9gb75dg7742dd359571": ["Brutal? Blood still flows through his own veins. I was positively <i>gentle.</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "7826c1d7-3f50-dfa5-afdb-774ca92390e4"], "hf4c69091gb421g4b2bg8cd3g0c70d4463d70": ["You're not going to eviscerate him? I was hoping for a show.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "7ffad86a-64d0-adf4-3694-ca03323e8b02"], "h8c54f85bgd102g4e80g98ecg1f2e17535718": ["Cool your blood - I'll indulge you soon enough. ", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "c0f4f5ff-9169-706e-8795-4a8b5b5477f2"], "hf3e5a1d3gf388g4040gbd77gcfd7722b3a04": ["I mislike your methods, gith. None should be made to live on their knees - even an enemy.", "0de603c5-42e2-4811-9dad-f652de080eba", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "6ec0e792-9e6e-defb-1d11-1e74b2e241cc"], "h445e6aa6g3dceg47b4g9890gca68fb566349": ["It is on his knees that he best served me. He should be grateful for the chance.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "012a187e-64e9-706d-814f-dfd05d437d81"], "h1dbd571ag75c2g47a5g931bg31a3e966d6ae": ["On your knees. She <i>won't</i> say it again.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "fb9f8fae-3c34-47cc-13c1-9ef7f26464b5"], "h8c624948g06b9g49cdg9075g22a08fa2fbaa": ["She's serious. You'd better get on you knees. <i>Fast</i>. ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "fb9f8fae-3c34-47cc-13c1-9ef7f26464b5"], "h0e24092eg4893g4331gb370g07577a9a01bd": ["That's enough, Lae'zel. I'll take it from here.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "fe720c04-06bf-833c-0e01-41eec6f326d6"], "h06f4912bg3af2g4e7fg803bg36eadb9ab466": ["You dare interrupt? Has the tadpole ravaged your senses?", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "adde3d48-ee0e-8752-2831-54fb2a42b2c3"], "h394cacf3g3305g4e05g9a9dg41fb849a436c": ["Fine - do as you must. But keep it quick.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "ce9f8609-1ccd-6df8-2934-ed198bb4692b"], "h64b79885g199eg4423gbf9eg46efc810067c": ["<i>Lower.</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "766495d9-94d8-2a91-4339-85ac9703a2a9"], "ha5427ba0g6e6bg4126g981cgec156c63148c": ["Enough, Lae'zel. You <i>will</i> be silent.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "695f8284-afde-f84f-de10-962006b12b98"], "h6ad013b8g2503g4b59g8737g80d5bf4161fb": ["Come on - stand up.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "0289b1c5-100d-99e8-d440-7a92a6938b65"], "h90fa6f1fg8347g4ebcgb41fg732fa1dd0a57": ["Th-thanks.", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "25e41bc2-9ada-568b-32d7-d9244f7d594a"], "hbab75b73gb04ag49c2ga7d0g4d1014a5745b": ["What do you want from m-me?", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "7da3d25f-1d7a-d392-3668-3191ae8c2e22"], "h067067b7g21a4g4251ga744g7e6e45c9915e": ["Information. Where did you see the githyanki?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "e8542e96-1b72-cd2d-2033-4f9a3c559303"], "h3f375372g723cg4abcg98d7g611dd1aaf3c4": ["On the road to Baldur's Gate, near the mountain p-pass.", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "d00975d9-7931-9561-afcc-71781ed3f423"], "h632ca2eag06fag41d8g8e5cge5c02110ca9e": ["Saw <i>us</i> 'fore we s-saw <i>it.</i> Jammed its b-b-blade through Yul's belly, straight to the other side.", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "3fe28776-7bdb-c2dc-7155-ea3d63f2c22a"], "hb6545128g36d0g4c65g9c74gc524589abd24": ["And I just... I just <i>ran.</i>", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "39576117-c979-b270-cb06-7974e4cd447e"], "h1cfa3564g51f3g4f0eg89fagdfca41e4195e": ["The map. Show me.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "8b9521d0-7171-732a-95f0-8d4021d00485"], "hda7f5f78g7089g498agb1fbg4dc6189910c0": ["Nothing. We're done with you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "6130a4b9-d4e9-60cc-1b61-c779e756ee9d"], "hbef2d54dg6659g416fg8fadgfa69096051c5": ["<i>K'chakhi!</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "840c734d-28e4-fde4-bac8-df74f5646d01"], "h4a615d4fgba06g4fbcgb590g84ddb662319b": ["You can breathe again. I won't let her hurt you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "5b891520-cf66-8749-393a-13cb19088de3"], "h511e39a6gb868g42fag9240g71e31bbac7fa": ["You - tell me where you saw the githyanki.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "ed251455-8895-b706-dae3-bc024ef89166"], "h2043ed3ag6f47g4ce6g8266g5550c049eed2": ["On the road to Baldur's Gate, near the mountain p-pass.", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "2c4a1036-fd1c-a3cc-ff41-700b2cbd30fb"], "h312839c8g86acg4771gb326g20ea74a11dc4": ["Saw <i>us</i> 'fore we s-saw <i>it.</i> Jammed its b-b-blade through Yul's belly, straight to the other side.", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "3efb97fb-e641-cad7-0533-82597c141ff7"], "h572f0507g4b9cg4999gb7d8geb485385e58b": ["And I just... I just <i>ran.</i>", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "c03e1aac-f829-5d6d-8299-0828bc6d14ac"], "hc32c5082g54c0g44a7g9425gf5975219dd18": ["The map. Show me.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "55d9caae-9145-8eac-1ce5-3c9e10652332"], "h91590a2dgb6bcg44aeg93e2g3cc428f73128": ["I'm sorry. She can be... harsh.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "d44af097-742f-a353-c491-bdd7eb491ae8"], "h14102fffg1ab1g40fagbb72g00a0ef1c45ea": ["No hard f-feelings.", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "ddc1dc8d-9de8-7778-2e80-220083d09b78"], "hf95c2f04g8c8fg453bgb4ddg222a629af6e4": ["Thanks for the information. You can get up.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "de71e5d1-717a-748c-26be-28be1ca245fa"], "h6d99d133g0b4cg48b2g8792ge9d4525aacfd": ["<i>Leave him bowing.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "72db7c54-d1f4-81f2-b3e0-73deca610fd2"], "hb2314961gf241g41d0gbe9ag5e60369b7658": ["Quit snivelling. We're done with you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "8ba164ee-7779-10b3-9ce9-49010455c4fe"], "hd917443dgae4eg4469gb344g9c1436a8682a": ["Just keep that th-thing away from me.", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "0a103e5b-c615-148f-0460-2e4c69a6bfbd"], "h529becb3gbfe0g4ab3g8fb3ga500ad5a1bfa": ["All right, Lae'zel. You got what you needed. ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "3016fa5e-05b0-5bf2-60cc-5b5f2cd65a04"], "h58dc22d5g408cg4539g8a0agd12d04f8a720": ["Yes. Your mediocre interrogation technique notwithstanding.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "16b6e3ec-36e4-f714-81da-734fa92ba70c"], "hb5f392e2g2d9fg4215gb4bag618e8d6b9a55": ["Yes. Your mediocre interrogation technique notwithstanding.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "19bc7f67-73e0-0286-d73e-b592aeeda237"], "h6d40d322gd478g44bdga3cfg204dd859da96": ["Up. You can keep your innards.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "0784c13a-c364-11ed-f882-c2aa79b4f974"], "he44cf308g45a5g4242ga131gbd8e5e1225bc": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "61e6dacc-6ed5-f01f-a6cb-55042074113c"], "h471fe015gb0dcg4e9egbb3fg3c714d254115": ["Stop. There is no honour in tormenting the defeated.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "f102e5c0-edd7-0350-482a-4350d4a7b9ae"], "h5dd2b2cbg2621g4449g86a9gec9887d02c10": ["Has the tadpole ravaged your senses? It is his suffering that will lead us to purity.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "a27b22ec-a513-6c19-a607-f09ba2214d89"], "h3c353420g29c5g49d4gb372gb8ca7f35402f": ["Stop it - he's suffered enough.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "584efced-069d-0155-d58f-b49eef635241"], "ha1ecbd93g91c1g4b6aga065gd35cbab7e13e": ["<i>Give the tiefling a menacing glare.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "8a85fe38-1ae6-6eb1-7b37-87587f22537a"], "hb736c3a0g27edg48bdg8a5fg7421496a84f3": ["You heard the woman. <i>Bow.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "8a85fe38-1ae6-6eb1-7b37-87587f22537a"], "h39f0141bg4a72g437agb098g516329e44aaf": ["Hold it, Lae'zel. I'll see to this one.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "b44e0397-1d35-2d9d-f11f-a42c7701681c"], "h490d97d5g7ba1g46ddgaa0cg39a1f6ecbb6b": ["You dare interrupt? Has the tadpole ravaged your senses?", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "86ce74ad-dda4-7932-bf99-84bc50a974f2"], "hde7a6109g0f89g4d42ga253g207b207a80e6": ["Fine - do as you must. But make it quick.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "d647be59-4c38-d15f-2efd-fa0f2698e123"], "hca6a170eg2617g48d3gb4b3gabf445527e96": ["<i>Bow.</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "c656d406-1e84-d17d-077e-87a2d59041db"], "h4b8ccb2aga5bdg4480g8cf7g30671d134d24": ["<i>Enough</i>. Stand down - I won't tell you again.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "c0bc17c7-7634-6957-8547-a2e0e7ed2ae9"], "h0fec3337ge3aeg4581gb23ag77e4b07ccfcc": ["<i>K'chakhi! </i>Fine.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "0453d88f-224e-2f9d-1859-fcd79dde78bf"], "h15dfff64gef5bg4671g956bgcf580a30aaff": ["You can breathe again. I won't let her hurt you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "4ffeb1f8-8431-6972-1b6a-39ec72ae5143"], "hd1cb4915g9743g45d8ga867g1203793011b9": ["Th-thanks.", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "8e5947ef-bb15-99b6-1974-40fab949ee17"], "h954459d9gc0c0g4d65g8acag7d81d0d05329": ["What do you want from m-me?", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "0282b9ba-71ff-cbfe-f53b-f84f3198636c"], "h343cab2eg18d4g4549g8e8eg619a80376356": ["Information. Where did you see the githyanki?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "38a595dd-12ca-3b58-ea03-3814addc9336"], "ha8ca1ab5g62f4g4d30ga3edgb1143b8f91dc": ["On the road to Baldur's Gate, near the mountain p-pass.", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "3f5f3640-f14b-6f60-65fc-36dfd13c94f6"], "h7d22dec1ga68ag43bdgae19g6731cb3c2185": ["Saw <i>us</i> 'fore we s-saw <i>it.</i> Jammed its b-b-blade through Yul's belly, straight to the other side.", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "fd7fddc1-1abb-d160-cfdf-f77d5066b8e6"], "hb520c752g3964g44d5g8a2dg0e23bceb184a": ["And I just... I just <i>ran.</i>", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "85bdbf01-086f-2ad9-5709-9121ae3b2612"], "hc25f9846gdfc8g4affg8297ge7f356078310": ["The map. Show me.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "84b91023-a195-800c-82dc-8c7712dc3553"], "h0770e212gc4e4g4c56ga622ga5db3c48387d": ["Nothing. We're done with you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "bf387807-2984-73e6-0298-b7aaf8eb9af1"], "hc0c2f3a2g14cfg4c64ga3e7g6e33f7fdfb95": ["<i>K'chakhi!</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "f85075ff-9b4d-490e-24dd-ef6d26c40352"], "ha5e0a1ceg2d98g4494gbf0fg4077c26795c7": ["You - tell me where you saw the githyanki.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "9cc93c77-9ffa-9037-0c99-e33f70bd7ce3"], "ha56fa8f2g119bg49adga4ffgb93b68af1203": ["On the road to Baldur's Gate, near the mountain p-pass.", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "e6e31bfd-f42b-a179-e360-dfd7a1e54f89"], "h0f2f552eg870fg4bd4g89e5g99affc6d09fa": ["Saw <i>us</i> 'fore we s-saw <i>it.</i> Jammed its b-b-blade through Yul's belly, straight to the other side.", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "f6f93697-9afa-ed61-1861-47594fbea95b"], "h37d39b21g09b2g4accga9beg83a454393374": ["And I just... I just <i>ran.</i>", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "3c94f6e9-f9e7-6842-a6b7-86ede37dae5a"], "h46591692g9ba6g454fg8308g5f53bb4beea2": ["The map. Show me.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "15bf8d55-8894-faae-3d41-aab7849e1f4d"], "hb24f7628ga315g4b1dgb5bdgf9f44cf33f07": ["Thanks for your help... and apologies for my companion.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "d6badd80-07af-595d-676d-cec1c2679b2d"], "hacad322dg5970g41b1g86c3gec8e3c892c13": ["No hard f-feelings.", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "e19a1f84-7d91-804a-9234-8716728bd151"], "ha0025b44g8a9eg4d84gb652g0aaa90503693": ["Quit your snivelling. We're done with you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "9a4c2ecd-fff3-22c0-7ec9-bc3da9358cd1"], "h4173bb31g9f7ag46d2g9417g79606b368fe1": ["Just keep that th-thing away from me.", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "7c70cc73-4230-8091-c6bf-cfb94833537d"], "h0455e91dgf095g4b1agbaecgb01fb526b2f8": ["All right, Lae'zel. You got what you needed. ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "b030a1e5-0cb9-af6f-3da3-400d46743c1a"], "h9ae2c65cgad0eg4038g8690g8fc2de16be32": ["Yes. Your mediocre interrogation technique notwithstanding.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "25557b20-b628-3c4e-20f5-2836c22d8a1b"], "hd7496238g9900g4fbag86edgdee0de4b01aa": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "c1a16009-d557-9407-1625-a15492cb3dac"], "h19f8b0b1g0753g465ag8793g64bfd0d064a9": ["Talk, tiefling. Where did you see another like her?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "12208f72-400b-3dff-23cd-66e022933eab"], "h6abf2bdbg0381g42d7g8659g9b26ba356a05": ["You shame yourself, Lae'zel. I denounce this cruelty!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "07b3156e-1d4b-c865-82a4-7154cf01dae2"], "ha90007b8g062eg4726gae75g92b79359a02a": ["I think we can resolve this with some decorum - don't you think?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "5f22ca52-c16a-c521-bace-bf0e5e72bac3"], "h40b0621age7f6g49c8gbb2fga4fc4abdb499": ["No.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "c53cf667-9f56-4e2f-d81b-56c04007260c"], "hc9eeec5eg3205g4cc3gb914gbe8493fac054": ["Go on. Bow.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "778c350e-356d-2997-11b8-ed05005a3057"], "h6e723685g1a20g4080g8da7gaaa7ec769a04": ["Show some sympathy, Lae'zel. He's terrified.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "6c91b0f2-6b79-c18a-9f55-ca138136470d"], "h9d531a0agdce4g4026ga64bg02398b48b816": ["Has the tadpole ravaged your senses? Sympathy will not lead us to purity.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_OM_Laezel_COM.html", "319f5f70-3d5b-2286-1ed0-b6dd6ec9684f"]}